  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink71-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">parattaiyarōṭu puṉalāṭiṉāṉ eṉak kēṭṭup pulanta talaimakaḷ talaimakaṉ
          ataṉai illai eṉṟu maṟaittuḻic colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink71">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>cūtār kuṟuntoṭic cūramai nuṭakkattu</l>
          <l>niṉveṅ kātali taḻīi nerunai</l>
          <l>yāṭiṉai yeṉpa puṉalē yalarē</l>
          <l>maṟaitta lollumō makiḻna</l>
          <l>putaitta lollumō ñāyiṟṟa toḷiyē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> They're saying that you bathed in the flood yesterday, </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> embracing your libidinous lover,</l>
          <l rend="indent4"> with a terrifying swinging of [her] small, circular bracelets – </l>
          <l> Can you conceal gossip [from me], you delightful man? </l>
          <l> Can you bury the brilliance of the sun? </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
